<HEADLINE> Zimbabwe's Major Dams Record Significant Gains </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, April 17 (xinhua) -- Most of Zimbabwe's major dams are
full as the country enjoys one of the best rainfall seasons in
years.
</P>
<P>
Statistics released today by the Water Department
show 37 of the country's dams are spilling while seven others are
more than 90 percent full, with most of them on the verge of
spilling.
</P>
<P>
As of Wednesday all the country's dams were 87.12 percent full.
