political leaders and candidates of all parties "must be accorded
the opportunity to give the necessary information to their
electorate to enable them make choices when they exercise their
rights to vote."
</P>
<P>
The Kenyan minister said that it was normal practice for
foreign embassies to raise their concerns with the government.
</P>
<P>
