concluded agreements to provide part of the financing for
building apartments along Mwinyi and Haile Selassie roads in the
city.
</P>
<P>
Undertaken by Theatre Square Ltd., the 5.5 million US Dollar
project will have 16 studio apartments, 22 one-bedroom apartments,
eight two-bedroom apartments, two three-bedroom apartments and
conference facilities for lefting to a high-level clientele.
</P>
<P>
Owners of the project are actors of the Little Theatre, Murray
Robertson of South Africa, OPK Holdings Ltd. of UK, and Protea Hotels
of South Africa who will also manage the venture.  enditem

