socio-economic policies which could fully utilize the potential to
improve the economic conditions.
</P>
<P>
The president hoped that the recent incentive packages
announced by the government for the agricultural and industrial
sectors would result increase in productivity, as Pakistan had
immense potential.
</P>
<P>
