Meanwhile, the Philippine team kept the overall lead in the
team competiton in the 2,465-kilometer race, with a total time of
23:21:22, five minutes and 8 seconds ahead of South Korea.
</P>
<P>
Third place went to Malaysia, which clocked at 23:47:05,
followed by Hong Kong (23:54:50), Indonesia (24:08:30) and Japan
(24:39:50). 
