increase good-neighborly and friendly cooperation between China
and the ASEAN, and had a full exchange of views on international
and regional issues.
</P>
<P>
This has increased mutual understanding and reached extensive
consensus through the consultation, both China and ASEAN expressed
satisfaction with the discussions and the current development of
ties between China and ASEAN.
</P>
<P>
Political consultations by the senior officials of the two
countries held annually in China and in the ASEAN nations are an
important part of the round of dialogues between China and ASEAN,
</P>
<P>
Hui Liangyu, Governor of Anhui Province, met with the
delegations.  
