<HEADLINE> National Flower Show Opens in Central Chinese City </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUOYANG, April 18 (Xinhua) -- A show of national and famous
flowers from 20 countries is being held in Luoyang, an ancient
city in central China's Henan Province.
</P>
<P>
This was the first show of national flowers of other countries
ever held in China.
</P>
<P>
The show was jointly organized by the China Association of
Flower Arranging Art and the Luoyang Bureau of Parks and Woods,
