-- The private transport owners have refused to haul the
procured wheat to Karachi as they have not been paid their
transportation dues for the last three years by the Sindh food
department.
</P>
<P>
The Muslim
</P>
<P>
-- Pakistani Prime Minister Nawaz Sharif said here Thursday
during a meeting with Chinese Ambassador Zhang Chengli that
Pakistan-China friendship has always stood test of times and it is
the corner stone of Pakistan's foreign policy.  
