<HEADLINE> Jing Leads Singapore to Commonwealth Title </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, April 17 (Xinhua) -- Beijing-born Jing Jun-hong led
Singapore to its first Commonwealth title after beating England
4-2 in Glascow on Thursday.
